content: I'm glad you helped me with the meal plan and grocery list. I think I'll stick to Instacart for this week's grocery shopping. By the way, I've been using their service quite frequently. I ordered from Publix last week and spent around $60. The delivery fee was $10, but it was worth it since I was short on time. Do you think you could help me estimate the cost of the ingredients on this list based on average prices? I'd like to budget for my groceries this week.
